Package: vigiar
Type: Package
Title: Download and Process VIGIAR Environmental Health Surveillance Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ryan",
           family = "Santos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "santosry@protonmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")),
    person(given = "vigiar",
           family = "team",
           role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides a programmatic interface to download and process
    the complete dataset from Brazil's VIGIAR (Vigilancia em Saude
    Ambiental) public Power BI dashboard, maintained by the Brazilian
    Ministry of Health. The package follows the microdatasus architecture
    with separate download and processing layers. It handles Power BI
    anonymous session management, automatic decompression of the DSR
    (Data Shape Response) format, standardises column names, validates
    IBGE municipality codes, and returns typed tibbles (vigiar_tbl) with
    metadata. Data includes PM2.5 air quality, population exposure,
    epidemiological health indicators, attributable fractions, and
    indoor solid fuel exposure. Includes a complete variable dictionary.
